		"name": "Fayrouza Ad AI Detector API",
		"description": "API collection for testing the Fayrouza Ad AI Detector backend. Includes all endpoints with example requests and responses.\n\n## Authentication\nAll protected endpoints require an `X-API-Key` header. There are three API key scopes:\n- **webhook**: Used for `POST /webhook/moderate`\n- **internal**: Used for `POST /api/ads/moderate`\n- **admin**: Used for `POST /api/admin/override` and `GET /api/admin/audit`\n\nSet your API keys in the collection variables before testing.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
